SetupWizard_FirstPage_Title.en_US: Welcome to the Tears of the Kingdom Mod Manager!

SetupWizard_FirstPage_Content.en_US:
This setup wizard will guide you through setting up TKMM to work with your computer.

Click the info button (i) in the bottom left at any time to get more information.

SetupWizard_Popup_InvalidEmulatorSelecti.en_US: Please choose one of the options before proceeding.

SetupWizard_EmulatorSelection_Title.en_US: How are you playing Tears of the Kingdom?

SetupWizard_EmulatorSelection_RyujinxOpt.en_US: Using a Ryujinx based emulator (Recommended on most hardware)

SetupWizard_EmulatorSelection_OtherOptio.en_US: Using another emulator (Only recommended for SteamDeck and weak hardware)

SetupWizard_RyujinxSetup_Content.en_US: Make sure you have the prod and title keys configured and have "The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom" installed with at least one update.

SetupWizard_MissingKeys_Content.en_US: The production keys (prod.keys) and/or title keys (title.keys) are missing, please reboot to Hekate and inject the Lockpick_RCM payload to dump them.
